    - "struct_extra118.zspec.zsdl — covers Struct method __objclass__ identity (name/module/qualname) and Struct.pack/__class__.__name__.__len__()==17 (table + invariants)."
    - "struct_extra96.zspec.zsdl — covers module-level function __name__.__len__() values for all six functions (table + invariants)."
    - "struct_extra95.zspec.zsdl — covers pack_into/unpack_from/iter_unpack __qualname__.__len__() and module-level function __module__.__eq__('_struct') (table + invariants)."
